---
title: Fig-Glazed Halloumi Bowl with Lemony Couscous and Garlic Sauce
description: Fig glazed halloumi nicely complements the roasted veggies in this delightful, summery bowl. Zesty couscous enlivens the whole experience, bringing that brightness that we love so much on a balmy  evening!
